---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/base_layout.astro";

const title = "Why Choose My Services";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={title}>
  <article aria-label={title}>
    <h1 transition:animate="slide">{title}?</h1>

    <div class="flex flex-column flex-wrap gap-4">
      <section
        class="grow w-full sm:w-1/3 sm:min-w-[300px] p-2 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-2 border-transparent hover:border-primary"
      >
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <Icon
            class="text-primary dark:text-primary-dark"
            name="responsive_design"
            size={50}
          />
          <h2 class="text-2xl">Responsive Design</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          I craft every project with a mobile-first mindset, ensuring a seamless
          user experience across a variety of devices. Responsive design is not
          just a feature, it's a fundamental aspect of my development
          philosophy.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section
        class="grow w-full sm:w-1/4 sm:min-w-[300px] p-2 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-2 border-transparent hover:border-primary"
      >
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <Icon
            class="text-primary dark:text-primary-dark"
            name="performance"
            size={50}
          />
          <h2 class="text-2xl">Performance Optimization</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          I understand the importance of performance. By implementing best
          practices, lazy loading, and code splitting and other optimization
          strategies I guarantee fast load times, smooth animations, and an
          overall enhanced user experience.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section
        class="grow w-full sm:w-1/3 sm:min-w-[300px] p-2 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-2 border-transparent hover:border-primary"
      >
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <Icon
            class="text-primary dark:text-primary-dark"
            name="cross_browser"
            size={50}
          />
          <h2 class="text-2xl">Cross-Browser Compatibility</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          I ensure compatibility with various browsers to provide a consistent
          experience for all users.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section
        class="grow w-full sm:w-1/4 sm:min-w-[300px] p-2 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-2 border-transparent hover:border-primary"
      >
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <Icon
            class="text-primary dark:text-primary-dark"
            name="innovation"
            size={50}
          />
          <h2 class="text-2xl">Innovative Approach</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          I bring a fresh and innovative approach to every project, ensuring
          that each solution is tailored to meet the unique needs and goals of
          my clients. By staying updated with the latest industry trends and
          technologies, I strive to deliver cutting-edge solutions.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section
        class="grow w-full sm:w-1/3 sm:min-w-[300px] p-2 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-2 border-transparent hover:border-primary"
      >
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-2xl">Client-centric</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          Every project is unique, and I take a client-centric approach to
          ensure that the solutions provided align with your specific
          objectives. Tailoring my services to your needs is a cornerstone of my
          development philosophy.
        </p>
        <p>
          Ultimately, client satisfaction is my top priority. I measure success
          not just by the completion of a project but by the satisfaction and
          success of my clients in achieving their goals.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section
        class="grow w-full sm:w-1/4 sm:min-w-[300px] p-2 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-2 border-transparent hover:border-primary"
      >
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <Icon
            class="text-primary dark:text-primary-dark"
            name="agile"
            size={50}
          />
          <h2 class="text-2xl">Agile Methodology</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          I embrace an agile development approach, allowing me to adapt to
          changing project requirements and deliver high-quality results
          efficiently. This iterative process ensures collaboration and
          transparency throughout the development lifecycle.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section
        class="grow w-full sm:w-1/3 sm:min-w-[300px] p-2 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-2 border-transparent hover:border-primary"
      >
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-2xl">Collaboration and Communication</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          Effective communication is the key to successful projects. I
          prioritize open and transparent communication with my clients,
          ensuring that every step of the development process is collaborative
          and aligned with client's vision vision.
        </p>
        <p>
          I thrive on collaborative problem-solving. Whether it's overcoming
          challenges during development or brainstorming creative solutions, I
          actively involve clients in the decision-making process.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section
        class="grow w-full sm:w-1/4 sm:min-w-[300px] p-2 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-2 border-transparent hover:border-primary"
      >
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <Icon
            class="text-primary dark:text-primary-dark"
            name="global_learning"
            size={50}
          />
          <h2 class="text-2xl">Continuous Learning</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          The tech landscape is dynamic, and I thrive on continuous learning.
          Staying updated with the latest trends and technologies allows me to
          provide clients with the most up-to-date solutions.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
